title: Spectre 2015 English Forced Subs [2h18m28s] v2
description:
This is an external English subtitle file, created to be usable with Spectre (2015) videos that are 2 hours, 18 minutes and 28 seconds long.

It contains reasonable translations for the foreign parts of the film only.

This is a re-release with corrections, hence the "v2". RAV3N is using a broken version of my subs with their crappy 1.5GB 480p release; BTCoop is using the fixed version with their earlier and higher quality 1.5GB 720p release.

Thanks BTCoop for alerting me to the errors in v1.

Feel free to alter this file, or share it, in any way that you choose
